| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0182 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 76da0fa0-7423-5ab9-9ebc-8f8bf4b97be8"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
